name: The End of An Age web
name_original: The End of An Age web
description:
Play as a dinosaur and resist the greatest extinction of mankind's species!

Move from left to right with your keyboard and avoid meteorites falling from the sky!

Recover powers to resist longer!

Enhance your powers to increase their frequency and efficiency with the coins you collect!

Fulfill goals to earn more coins!
